content.description:
Per flagstaffmountainbouldering.blogspot.com: "start at the incut jug on the left side of the wall where #4 (

North Overhang Traverse

) starts, pull hard up to a right hand edge, and move left to the lip. From there, reach over the lip with your right hand to a pebble, then paddle up pebbles and cobbles to safety."
